<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>Bb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Pathian fa hna tho u! temtawntu ngeiloin, Kan bawi bik cu lungthin
 nunnak thazang dihlak pe u.

[V2]
 Pathian fa hna tho u! A pennak rau hmanh seh, Nan palhnak kaltak in
 u-nau dawtnak lungthin ngei u.

[V3]
 Pathian fa hna tho u! Nan Khrihfabu ca-ah, Nan Khrihfabu rian
 hlawhtlin awkah tho u law tuan u.

[V4]
 Khrih vailam cu put in, A keneh cu zul u, Khrih unau chuakkhat
 lungthin he tho u, Pathian fa hna.</lyrics>
<title>PATHIAN FA HNA THO U CH9</title>
<hymn_number>9</hymn_number>
</song>